Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba ya yi tsokaci game da wani shafi da aka biya a shafinsa na Des Moines Register, wata jaridar kasar Sin da ta fi yawan kudade a Iowa, inda ya zargi kasar Sin da yin katsalandan a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka da aka yi ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ke yi na cewa kasar Sin ba ta da gaskiya.
