2004: Babban girgizar kasa a yankin Aceh da ke yammacin tekun Indonesia ya faru a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba, ya shafi kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a yankin Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
