Syria ta ce a shirye take ta karɓi 'yan gudun hijira da son ransu kuma ta nemi taimako don sake gina ƙasar da ta lalace a cikin shekaru bakwai na yaƙi.
Da yake jawabi a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Mouallem ya ce, "yanayin da ake ciki a kasar na ingantawa.
"A yau, saboda ci gaba da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci, an sami kwanciyar hankali da tsaro a yankin", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gina wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin dawo da rayuwa yadda take a baya.
A yau, akwai dukkan hanyoyin da za a iya dawo da 'yan gudun hijira zuwa kasashen da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da takunkumin tattalin arziki da ya shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Ƙungiyar Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa, tun bayan da aka fara yaƙin a shekara ta 2011, fiye da 'yan Siriya miliyan biyar da dubu hamsin ne suka bar ƙasarsu.
Sauran mutane miliyan shida da suke zaune a kasar na bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Mu'alim ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi maraba da taimakon da ake samu don sake gina kasar da aka lalata.
Amma ya ce ba zai amince da taimako ko tallafi daga kasashen da suka dauki nauyin tawayen ba.
Turai ta yi murna da nasarar da ta yi a gasar cin kofin Ryder a Paris
Tawagar Turai ta lashe kofin Ryder a 2018 bayan ta doke ta Amurka da 16.5-10.5 a Le Golf National da ke wajen Paris.
A yanzu haka Amurka ta sha kashi shida a jere a gasar Turai kuma ba ta yi nasara ba a gasar Ryder a Turai a shekarar 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kofin bayan da tawagar Thomas Bjorn ta Denmark ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata don kayar da Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Nicholson, wanda ya yi fama da kusan dukkanin gasar, ya jefa kwallo a cikin ruwa a karo na uku, ya rasa wasan a wasan 16 da Francesco Molinari.
Golferin Italiya Molinari ya haskaka a zagaye-zagaye, yana ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka ci 5-0-0 tun daga 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spitt ya zira kwallaye 5 da 4 a wasan da dan wasan Denmark Thorbjørn Olesen, dan wasan da ya fi rashin nasara a gasar zakarun Turai.
Dustin Johnson, wanda shi ne ɗan wasa mafi ƙanƙanta a duniya, ya doke ɗan wasan Ingila, Paul Poulter, da ya yi nasara da ci biyu da ɗaya, kuma wannan shi ne karo na ƙarshe da ya yi gasar Ryder.
